[I] The MATE Terminal Emulator

[T] This is the MATE terminal emulator application. mate-terminal is only the
[T] shell (menubar, prefs dialog); the terminal emulation comes from the VTE
[T] widget. MATE terminal is a fork of GNOME terminal.

[U] https://mate-desktop.org/

[A] MATE developer
